{"tid":518450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無間道?】朱經緯辯方大狀：3個月刑期唔係重","createTime":"2018-01-03T10:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T11:14:47.000Z","uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f70b6381544a589e15a700dfbf735eea8db1e08d","tid":518450,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57660932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57660932&d=ryJDW5LW9OMZ1e8iLawrI26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2fb7f92a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57660932&h=59cf754e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57660932</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">於本案代表朱經緯辯護的大律師彭彼得，於庭外以案件將會上訴為由，拒絕深入評論，但明言覺得判囚3個月「唔係重」。</span><br />\n<br />\n彭離庭時回應傳媒提問，稱報告建議判處朱經緯接受社會服務令，他認為應跟從報告判刑，「個sentence（判刑）呢，其實就唔係重嘅，但我覺得未必需要（判囚）囉。」他估計，朱因早前候判時已還柙十多天，加上一般的扣減，刑期尚餘一個半月左右，但因朱已獲保釋等候上訴，暫不再作評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連辯方大狀都唔覺得3個月刑期係重<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇怕你著起啡色囚衣嘅日子遲早會嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8572dbbcdb761a85fc156071b7ea4131461ee993","tid":518450,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c0ef0408ac56f6b940563c5244650179cf51d8","tid":518450,"uid":10905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"罪成之下3個月真係唔係重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d084eea77e03d6f349e803d0cf6bc456892e0","tid":518450,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"咁又係呀 唔小休班警都判多過3個月"},{"pid":"a6626c4467a185d71001906a577902a8909d1738","tid":518450,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"2個月走得啦，扣假，之前又坐左成個星期"},{"pid":"d0f7948f80d59fdfacc78cf8fcd668d218382d59","tid":518450,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"等陣個律師又比藍屍咬佢唔係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}